#: ../../../getting_started.rst:23
msgid ""
"These requirements can be easily installed on most modern Linux systems; on "
"macOS, the Command Line Tools package is required, and a full XCode suite "
"may be necessary for some packages such as Qt and apple-gl. Spack is "
"designed to run on HPC platforms like Cray.  Not all packages should be "
"expected to work on all platforms."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../getting_started.rst:29
msgid ""
"A build matrix showing which packages are working on which systems is shown "
"below."
